SubjectOrder Authorizing the Issue of Two Two-dollar Commemorative Circulation Coins Specifying the Characteristics and Determining the Designs (National Indigenous Peoples Day)
PrecisOrder authorizing the Royal Canadian Mint to produce TWO TWO-DOLLAR commemorative circulation coins, representing the cultural heritage and symbols of the Métis, First Nations, and Inuit communities to celebrate NATIONAL INDIGENOUS PEOPLES DAY.
